genotype
Class Tree

java.lang.Object
  genotype.Genotype
      genotype.Tree

public class Tree
extends Genotype

Tree genotype implementation. This class represents the genotype of an individual as a tree. holder is a pointer to the root of the tree, where the root and all other nodes in the tree are instances of TreeNode. This level of indirection allows the entire tree to change without creating a new @ Tree} instance.

Author:
Owen Derby
